Interface Advice.Dispatcher.OffsetMapping

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Advice.Dispatcher.OffsetMapping.ForBoxedArguments, Advice.Dispatcher.OffsetMapping.ForBoxedReturnValue, Advice.Dispatcher.OffsetMapping.ForEnterValue, Advice.Dispatcher.OffsetMapping.ForField, Advice.Dispatcher.OffsetMapping.ForField.WithExplicitType, Advice.Dispatcher.OffsetMapping.ForField.WithImplicitType, Advice.Dispatcher.OffsetMapping.ForInstrumentedType, Advice.Dispatcher.OffsetMapping.ForOrigin, Advice.Dispatcher.OffsetMapping.ForParameter, Advice.Dispatcher.OffsetMapping.ForReturnValue, Advice.Dispatcher.OffsetMapping.ForStubValue, Advice.Dispatcher.OffsetMapping.ForThisReference, Advice.Dispatcher.OffsetMapping.ForThrowable, Advice.Dispatcher.OffsetMapping.ForUnusedValue, Advice.Dispatcher.OffsetMapping.ForUserValue
    Enclosing interface:
    Advice.Dispatcher

    public static interface Advice.Dispatcher.OffsetMapping
    Represents an offset mapping for an advice method to an alternative offset.
